print.simulation

Class Server

  • java.lang.Object
    • print.simulation.Server

  • public class Server
extends java.lang.Object
    Server.java A class representing a printer that can service one print task at a time using Gaussian distributions to mirror realistic parameters that could be passed to a printer. 
        Project: print.simulation
    Platform: jdk 1.6.0_14; NetBeans IDE 6.8; Mac OSx
    Course: CS 143
    Hours: 2 hours
    Created on May 25th, 2013, 10:00:00 PM
    See Also:
    Client, PrintSimulationGUI, Queue, Random
